SDIOS_ASYNC_T_ Struct Reference

This structure defines the asynchronous I/O descriptor type.

Data Fields

  • int iUsingCallback
  • SDIOS_IO_CALLBACKROUTINE_T * callback_routine

Field Documentation

int SDIOS_ASYNC_T_::iUsingCallback

Set to SDIOS_TRUE if the application is going to use the callback method of confirming the result. Set to SDIOS_FALSE if the application is going to use the GetResult method.

SDIOS_IO_CALLBACKROUTINE_T* SDIOS_ASYNC_T_::callback_routine

Pointer to SCBS Callback routine.

void* SDIOS_ASYNC_T_::callback_context

Pointer to private context for callback routine.
